# Data Transformation Guidelines

When transforming MeteoSwiss data:

- Use Zod schemas for validation during transformation
- Maintain proper type definitions between raw data and schema data
- Follow the data schema defined in docs/analysis/data-schema.md
- Cache appropriately based on data update frequency

